安装nginx 依赖:
openssl
zlib
pcre
ngix

1.安装openssl
./config
make
make install


2.安装zlib
./configure 
make
make install


3.安装pcre
 ./configure 
make
make install

4.安装nginx
./configure --with-pcre=/home/pcre2-10.21/ --with-zlib=/home/zlib-1.2.10/ --with-openssl=/home/openssl-master/
make
make install


如果nginx 加入pcre库时编译错误，解决方法:
yum -y install pcre-devel

./configure  --with-zlib=/home/zlib-1.2.10/ --with-openssl=/home/openssl-master/
make
make install


5.监测Nginx是否安装成功
cd /usr/local/nginx/sbin/
./nginx -t

6.Nginx启动及看端口
 ./nginx
 netstat -ntlp  Nginx默认端口为80

 关闭nginx 
 ./nginx -s stop

 访问
 http://192.168.200.132/
